## Visualizacion

You can include R code in the document as follows:

```{r cars}


library(oRden)

data <- datos::mtautos
data %>% resumir(avg = mean(millas))



summary(cars)
# 
# library(tidyverse)
# 
# lsf.str("package:dplyr")
# 
# library(datos)
# 
data <- datos::mtautos
# 
library(oRden)
data %>% summarise(avg = mean(millas))
